          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Route to Opportunity And Development Act of 2015 or the ROAD Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Amends the Intermodal Surface Transportation Efficiency Act of 1991, as amended, to revise the high priority Raleigh-Norfolk Corridor of the National Highway System between Raleigh, North Carolina, and Norfolk, Virginia, to include Rocky Mount, Williamston, and Elizabeth City, North Carolina.</p>]]></text>
